   VERSION=( "0.59r" )
  CATEGORY="audio-player"
 ATTRIBUTE="broken console unsafe"
  HOMEPAGE="http://www.mpg123.de"
       URL="http://www.mpg123.de/mpg123"
 FRESHMEAT="mpg123"
     SHORT="mpg123 is an audio player, with security issues."
stream << EOF
mpg123 is a fast, free and portable MPEG audio player for Unix.
It supports MPEG 1.0/2.0 layers 1, 2 and 3.

It is believed this mpg123 is no longer maintained and may
have buffer overflow exploits that allow a remote
attacker to execute arbitrary code on the victim's machnie.

Use mpg321 instead.
EOF
